headline.main: No. 16 Miami Women Beat 8th-Ranked Florida State 56-54
headline.print_headline: No. 16 Miami Women Beat 8th-Ranked Florida State 56-54

lead_paragraph: Interpol says a three-week operation to tackle the illegal trade in wildlife and timber in 43 countries has led to the seizure of $5.1 million worth of illicit products from wild cats to sea horses and the identification of nearly 900 suspects.
